International Oil Limited



































HomeAbout UsProductsContact Us









Home










    International Oil Limited is the logistic subsidiary of AP&G group. The company is involved in logistics of all petroleum products such as petrol, diesel, LPG and aviation fuels to other subsidiaries of AP&G group; Afghan National Petroleum, Sun Gas, and Sun Petrol. As logistics is one of the key factors of an organization’s success and effectiveness, International Oil Limited is specialized in and is dedicated to the task of just in time logistics for the AP&G group based in Afghanistan. 





About US



	In this globalized world where placing the product effectively in the market is one of the most important key factors of marketing; such as delivering the right product to the right place at the right time, is the most important responsibility of logistics and we take it very seriously. 

We offer logistic services to AP&G group subsidiaries located in
Afghanistan to acquire CIS country products at competitive prices for the
Afghanistan market. Our operations include accurate logistics by choosing
the right supplier with the right type of products and adequate supplies,
and aggressive procurement. International Oil delivers products on time by
means of accurate planning, and inspection of products.

Our logistics team is dedicated to serve AP&G group subsidiaries in a very effective and timely manner, regularly and steadily since 2004. With our dedicated team work throughout the entire organization while constantly applying Total Quality Management (T.Q.M.), our company has a history of just in time and on time delivery of right products to the right place and with the best value.

We strive to perform at our highest level when distributing and marketing petroleum products to Afghanistan.


    
	



