                            Company Profile












AP Oil, a Singapore public Listed Lubricants Manufacturer in Singapore incorporated in 1975 produces a wide range of lubricants for automotive, industrial and marine applications. Our Lubricant products are largely marketed under the brand name of AP and Sino (Singapore Oil).   With advanced lube technology and the latest formulations, our lubricants are manufactured and closely quality controlled to meet the standards and specifications set by internationally-recognized institutions and organization namely API, SAE, MIL-L, ISOP, JASO and ASTM. We are an American Petroleum Institute (API) authorized license holder.   AP Oil produces a wide range of products which are applicable for:   1) Marine Lubricants: Include Marine Engine Oils, Marine Cylinder Oil, Marine Outboard Engine Oils, Stern Tube oil, Wire Rope oil etc.   2) Automotive Engine Oils: A Wide range of Gasoline Engine Oils & Diesel Engine Oils etc.   3) Industrial Lubricants: Chain Oils, Circulating Oils, Compressor Oils, Gear Oils, Hydraulic Oils, Turbine Oils, Machinery Oils etc.   4) Metal Working Fluids: Neat Cutting Oils, Soluble Cutting Oils, Stamping Oils etc.   5) Specialty Oils & Fluid: Heat Transfer Oils, Quenching Oils, Refrigerator Oils, Transformer Oils, Slideway Oils, Vacuum Pump Oils etc.   6) Greases: Lithium Complex Grease, MP Grease, MP-EP Grease, Moly Grease, Calcium Base Grease and Chassis Grease etc.




